lwindesk (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Wayland compositor based on wlroots 0.17 with scene-graph API
  * Server-side window decorations with cairo/pango title bar rendering
  * Qt6/QML shell with centered taskbar (48px bottom strip)
  * Start menu with application grid and search functionality
  * Window snap layouts and snap zones
  * Virtual desktop switching
  * Notification center and quick settings panel
  * System tray with clock widget
  * Desktop wallpaper support
  * Right-click desktop context menu
  * Keyboard shortcuts: Super key, Alt+Tab, and more
  * GDM session integration via wayland-sessions desktop file
  * XWayland support for X11 application compatibility

 -- Frank Kahle <frank@lwindesk.org>  Sat, 21 Feb 2026 12:00:00 -0400
